data.description: Quailbrook East premieres this Lovely 3 Bed 2.5 Bath Townhouse in desirable Somerset, ready and waiting for you. Just pack your bags and move right in! Foyer entry welcomes you in to find NEW Bamboo Flooring throughout. The light & bright Living Rm holds sliding glass doors giving way to the rear deck. Beautifully updated Kitchen offers SS Appliances, Quartz Counters, Glass Subway Tile Backsplash, & a plethora of premium cabinetry. Formal Dining Rm is perfect for hosting dinner guests. 1/2 Bath on this main level is so convenient! Upstairs, the main full bath + 3 Generous Bedrooms including the Master Suite. Master Bedroom boasts a WIC and sleek private ensuite Bath with Stall Shower. Doing Laundry is a breeze having the amenities on this level. Relax outdoors on the large Deck. 1 Car Garage & Driveway offer ample parking space. Enjoy the amenities in the community while being conveniently close to area shopping & dining. Truly, a MUST SEE! **Showings Begin 4/7/2024**
